il</h3>\n              <p>tomas.radic00@gmail.com</p>\n\n              <h3>Website</h3>\n              <a>https://radicc.github.io/Portfolio/</a>\n\n              <h3>Address</h3>\n              <p>Malacky, Slovakia</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"RightPaper\">\n            <div className=\"NameTitul\">\n              <h1>TOMÁŠ RADIČ</h1>\n              <p>SELFTHOUGHT FRONTEND DEVELOPER</p>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"AboutMe\">\n              <h3>ABOUT ME</h3>\n              <p>\n                I am a selfthouhgt student of frontend developing trying to\n                change profession. Experienced in HTML,CSS and JavaScript\n                specializing in ReactJS library. Implementing CSS-extansion SASS\n                and JavaScript-syntactical superset TypeScript.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"AboutMe\">\n              <h3>WORK EXPERIENCE</h3>\n              <p>\n                I am a selfthouhgt student of frontend developing trying to\n                change profession. Experienced in HTML,CSS and JavaScript\n                specializing in ReactJS library. Implementing CSS-extansion SASS\n                and JavaScript-syntactical superset TypeScript.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"AboutMe\">\n              <h3>SOFTWARE SKILL</h3>\n              <p>\n                I am a selfthouhgt student of frontend developing trying to\n                change profession. Experienced in HTML,CSS and JavaScript\n                specializing in ReactJS library. Implementing CSS-extansion SASS\n                and JavaScript-syntactical superset TypeScript.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div className=\"Footer1\">\n        <a\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer1\"\n          href=\"https://github.com/Radicc\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n        >\n          <img\n            className=\"footerSocial\"\n            src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/25/25231.png\"\n          />\n          <p className=\"footerText\">GitHub</p>\n        </a>\n        <a\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer2\"\n          href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tom%C3%A1%C5%A1-radi%C4%8D-068044221/\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n        >\n          <img\n            className=\"footerSocial\"\n            src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/174/174857.png\"\n          />\n          <p className=\"footerText\">LinkedIn</p>\n        </a>\n        <a\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer3\"\n          href=\"https://twitter.com/TomRadi1\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n        >\n          <img\n            className=\"footerSocial\"\n            src=\"https://www.pngkey.com/png/full/2-27646_twitter-logo-png-transparent-background-logo-twitter-png.png\"\n          />\n          <p className=\"footerText\">Twitter</p>\n        </a>\n        <a\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer4\"\n          href=\"https://www.instagram.com/radic.o_o/\"\n          target=\"_blank\"\n        >\n          <img\n            className=\"footerSocial\"\n            src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Instagram_icon.png/640px-Instagram_icon.png\"\n          />\n          <p className=\"footerText\">Instagram</p>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"Footer2\">\n        <a>MAIL ME NOW!</a>\n        <img src={Mail} />\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"Footer3\">\n        <p>© Copyright 2022, Tomas Radic All Rights Reserved.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n","C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Portfolio\\src\\myProjects.js",["241","242"],[],"import React from \"react\";\nimport \"./App.css\";\nimport \"./Cv.scss\";\nimport Project from \"./project.jpg\";\nimport Project2 from \"./project2.jpg\";\n\nexport default function MyProjects() {\n  return (\n    <div id=\"Projects\" className=\"myProjectsBody\">\n      <h1 className=\"projectsText\">Projects</h1>\n      <div className=\"projectBox1\">\n        <img className=\"imgBox1\" src={Project} alt=\"error\"></img>\n        <div className=\"projectContainer\">\n          <h2>MY PORTFOLIO</h2>\n          <p className=\"textBox1\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque sed\n            turpis in urna lacinia luctus. Phasellus placerat tempor urna nec\n            condimentum. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et\n            ultrices posuere cubilia curae; Fusce dignissim tempus vestibulum.\n            Aenean sed imperdiet ex. Etiam nisi eros, consectetur in venenatis\n            nec, congue fermentum augue. Aenean tristique viverra metus, vel\n            suscipit diam egestas ut. Nam scelerisque ipsum in lacinia placerat.\n            Nullam id posuere massa, sit amet rhoncus nulla. Morbi suscipit urna\n            vitae tellus viverra, sed scelerisque odio ultrices.\n          </p>\n          <div className=\"Cvbutton2\">\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            VISIT NOW!\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"projectBox2\">\n        <img className=\"imgBox2\" src={Project2}></img>\n        <div className=\"projectContainer2\">\n          <h2>ESHOP</h2>\n          <p className=\"textBox2\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque sed\n            turpis in urna lacinia luctus. Phasellus placerat tempor urna nec\n            condimentum. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et\n            ultrices posuere cubilia curae; Fusce dignissim tempus vestibulum.\n            Aenean sed imperdiet ex. Etiam nisi eros, consectetur in venenatis\n            nec, congue fermentum augue. Aenean tristique viverra metus, vel\n            suscipit diam egestas ut. Nam scelerisque ipsum in lacinia placerat.\n            Nullam id posuere massa, sit amet rhoncus nulla. Morbi suscipit urna\n            vitae tellus viverra, sed scelerisque odio ultrices.\n          </p>\n\n          <div className=\"Cvbutton2\">\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            VISIT NOW!\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"projectBox1\">\n        <img className=\"imgBox1\" src={Project}></img>\n        <div className=\"projectContainer\">\n          <h2>ESHOP</h2>\n          <p className=\"textBox1\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque sed\n            turpis in urna lacinia luctus. Phasellus placerat tempor urna nec\n            condimentum. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et\n            ultrices posuere cubilia curae; Fusce dignissim tempus vestibulum.\n            Aenean sed imperdiet ex. Etiam nisi eros, consectetur in venenatis\n            nec, congue fermentum augue. Aenean tristique viverra metus, vel\n            suscipit diam egestas ut. Nam scelerisque ipsum in lacinia placerat.\n            Nullam id posuere massa, sit amet rhoncus nulla. Morbi suscipit urna\n            vitae tellus viverra, sed scelerisque odio ultrices.\n          </p>\n          <div className=\"Cvbutton2\">\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            VISIT NOW!\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n","C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\index.js",[],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\App.js",["243"],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\reportWebVitals.js",[],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\Slider.js",["244"],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\myProjects.js",["245","246"],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\tooler.js",["247","248","249","250","251","252","253","254","255","256"],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\nav.js",["257","258","259","260","261","262","263","264"],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\Portfolio\\Main\\Portfolio\\src\\Footer.js",["265","266","267","268","269","270","271","272","273","274","275","276"],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\index.js",[],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\reportWebVitals.js",[],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\myProjects.js",["277","278"],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\jsx\\App.js",["279"],[],"import \"../css/App.css\";\r\nimport \"../css/Header.css\";\r\nimport \"../css/ToolsBar.css\";\r\nimport \"../css/ProjectsBody.css\";\r\n\r\nimport Slider from \"./Slider\";\r\nimport Nav from \"./nav\";\r\nimport Tooler from \"./tooler\";\r\nimport MyProjects from \"../myProjects\";\r\nimport Footer from \"./Footer\";\r\nimport Programmer from \"../images/programmer2.png\";\r\nimport { useState } from \"react\";\r\n\r\nfunction App() {\r\n  const [CV, setCV] = useState(\"CvForm-Footer2None\");\r\n  const [Mailos, setMail] = useState(\"contactBackgroundNone\");\r\n\r\n  return (\r\n    <div id=\"Home\" className=\"App\">\r\n      <div className=\"header\">\r\n        <Nav setCV={setCV} setMail={setMail} />\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div className=\"introduction\">\r\n        <div className=\"container\">\r\n          <div className=\"divTomRad\">\r\n            <div className=\"divHi\">\r\n              <h2 className=\"tomRadHi\">✌ Hi There! I'm Radicc</h2>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h1 className=\"tomRadText\">A Frontend developer</h1>\r\n            <h3 className=\"tomRadUnderText\">\r\n              Passionate junior front-end developer with a desire to learn and\r\n              grow in a collaborative team environment. Skilled in HTML, CSS,\r\n              and JavaScript. Specializing in ReactJS library.\r\n            </h3>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div className=\"notSliderContainer\">\r\n            <img className=\"notSliderImg\" src={Programmer} />\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <Slider />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <Tooler />\r\n      <MyProjects />\r\n\r\n      <Footer CV={CV} Mailos={Mailos} setCV={setCV} setMail={setMail} />\r\n    </div>\r\n  );\r\n}\r\nexport default App;\r\n","C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\jsx\\tooler.js",["280","281","282","283","284","285","286","287","288","289","290","291","292","293","294"],[],"import React, { Component } from \"react\";\r\nimport \"../css/App.css\";\r\n\r\nimport HTMLlogo from \"../images/HTML5logo.png\";\r\nimport CSSlogo from \"../images/CSS3logo.png\";\r\nimport SASSlogo from \"../images/SASSlogo.png\";\r\nimport JSlogo from \"../images/JSlogo.png\";\r\nimport TSlogo from \"../images/TSlogo.png\";\r\nimport REACTlogo from \"../images/REACTlogo.png\";\r\nimport WEBPACKlogo from \"../images/WEBPACKlogo.png\";\r\nimport GITlogo from \"../images/GITlogo.png\";\r\n\r\nexport default function Tooler() {\r\n  return (\r\n    <div className=\"toolsBar\">\r\n      <img className=\"toolsLogo\" src={HTMLlogo} />\r\n\r\n      <img className=\"toolsLogo\" src={CSSlogo} />\r\n\r\n      <img className=\"toolsLogo\" src={SASSlogo} />\r\n\r\n      <img className=\"toolsLogo\" src={JSlogo} />\r\n\r\n      <img className=\"toolsLogo\" src={REACTlogo} />\r\n\r\n      <img className=\"toolsLogo\" src={GITlogo} />\r\n      <div className=\"div1\">\r\n        <img className=\"toolsLogo2\" src={HTMLlogo} />\r\n\r\n        <img className=\"toolsLogo2\" src={CSSlogo} />\r\n\r\n        <img className=\"toolsLogo2\" src={JSlogo} />\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div className=\"div2\">\r\n        <img className=\"toolsLogo2\" src={REACTlogo} />\r\n\r\n        <img className=\"toolsLogo2\" src={SASSlogo} />\r\n\r\n        <img className=\"toolsLogo2\" src={GITlogo} />\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  );\r\n}\r\n","C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\jsx\\nav.js",["295","296","297","298","299","300","301","302"],[],"import React from \"react\";\r\nimport { useState } from \"react\";\r\n\r\nimport \"../css/BurgerMenu.css\";\r\nimport \"../css/Header.css\";\r\n\r\nimport gitHub from \"../images/GitHub.png\";\r\nimport linkedIN from \"../images/linkedIN.png\";\r\nimport twitter from \"../images/twitterLogo.png\";\r\nimport instagram from \"../images/instagram.png\";\r\n\r\nexport default function Nav(props) {\r\n  const [Active, IsActive] = useState(\"off\");\r\n  const [Style, setStyle] = useState(\"pushMenuHidden\");\r\n  const [Burger, setBurger] = useState(\"\");\r\n\r\n  const handleClick3 = () => {\r\n    IsActive(\"off\");\r\n    setStyle(\"pushMenuHidden\");\r\n    setBurger(\"\");\r\n    props.setCV(\"CvForm-Footer2\");\r\n  };\r\n  const handleClick2 = () => {\r\n    IsActive(\"off\");\r\n    setStyle(\"pushMenuHidden\");\r\n    setBurger(\"\");\r\n    props.setMail(\"contactBackgroundFlex\");\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  const handleClick = () => {\r\n    if (Active === \"off\") {\r\n      IsActive(\"true\");\r\n      setStyle(\"pushMenuDown\");\r\n      setBurger(\"open\");\r\n    } else {\r\n      IsActive(\"off\");\r\n      setStyle(\"pushMenuHidden\");\r\n      setBurger(\"\");\r\n    }\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  return (\r\n    <div className=\"headerContainer\">\r\n      <div onClick={handleClick} id=\"nav-icon2\" className={Burger}>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <a className=\"Radicc\" href=\"#Home\">\r\n        RADICC\r\n      </a>\r\n\r\n      <div className={Style}>\r\n        <div className=\"containerNav\">\r\n          <div className=\"greenBox\"></div>\r\n          <ul className=\"ulNav\">\r\n            <li>\r\n              <a onClick={handleClick} href=\"#Home\">\r\n                Home\r\n              </a>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n              <a onClick={handleClick} href=\"#Projects\">\r\n                Portfolio\r\n              </a>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n              <a onClick={handleClick3} href=\"#cvButt\">\r\n                CV\r\n              </a>\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li>\r\n              <a onClick={handleClick2} href=\"#Contact\">\r\n                Contact\r\n              </a>\r\n            </li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div className=\"containerSocial\">\r\n          <a\r\n            className=\"social1\"\r\n            href=\"https://github.com/Radicc\"\r\n            target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >\r\n            <img className=\"imgSocial\" src={gitHub} />\r\n            <p className=\"socialText\">GitHub</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          <a\r\n            className=\"social2\"\r\n            href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tomas-radicc/\"\r\n            target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >\r\n            <img className=\"imgSocial\" src={linkedIN} />\r\n            <p className=\"socialText\">LinkedIn</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          <a\r\n            className=\"social3\"\r\n            href=\"https://twitter.com/TomRadi1\"\r\n            target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >\r\n            <img className=\"imgSocial\" src={twitter} />\r\n            <p className=\"socialText\">Twitter</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n\r\n          <a\r\n            className=\"social4\"\r\n            href=\"https://www.instagram.com/radic.o_o/\"\r\n            target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >\r\n            <img className=\"imgSocial\" src={instagram} />\r\n            <p className=\"socialText\">Instagram</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  );\r\n}\r\n","C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\jsx\\Slider.js",[],[],"C:\\Users\\Radicc\\Desktop\\PROFILE\\profile\\src\\jsx\\Footer.js",["303","304","305","306","307","308","309","310","311","312","313"],[],"import { useState } from \"react\";\r\nimport \"../css/App.css\";\r\nimport \"../css/Footer.css\";\r\nimport \"../css/Header.css\";\r\nimport Mail from \"../images/mail.png\";\r\nimport \"../css/CvButton.scss\";\r\nimport \"../css/ContactSubmit.scss\";\r\n\r\nimport gitHub from \"../images/GitHub.png\";\r\nimport linkedIN from \"../images/linkedIN.png\";\r\nimport twitter from \"../images/twitterLogo.png\";\r\nimport instagram from \"../images/instagram.png\";\r\nimport avatar from \"../images/Tom1.jpg\";\r\n\r\nexport default function Footer(props) {\r\n  //const [show, setShow] = useState(\"CvForm-Footer2None\");\r\n  const [ide, setIde] = useState(\"cvButt\");\r\n\r\n  //const [contact, setContact] = useState(\"contactBackgroundNone\");\r\n\r\n  const showCv = () => {\r\n    if (props.CV === \"CvForm-Footer2None\") {\r\n      props.setCV(\"CvForm-Footer2\");\r\n      setTimeout(() => setIde(\"ide\"), 2000);\r\n    } else {\r\n      props.setCV(\"CvForm-Footer2None\");\r\n      setIde(\"cvButt\");\r\n    }\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  const showContact = () => {\r\n    if (props.Mailos === \"contactBackgroundNone\") {\r\n      props.setMail(\"contactBackgroundFlex\");\r\n    } else {\r\n      props.setMail(\"contactBackgroundNone\");\r\n    }\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  return (\r\n    <div className=\"containerFooter\">\r\n      <div className=\"buttonContainer\">\r\n        <a id=\"cvButt\" href={\"#\" + ide} onClick={showCv} className=\"Cvbutton\">\r\n          <span></span>\r\n          <span></span>\r\n          <span></span>\r\n          <span></span>\r\n          CV\r\n        </a>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div id=\"ide\" className={props.CV}>\r\n        <div className=\"WhitePaper\">\r\n          <div className=\"LeftPaper\">\r\n            <img className=\"CvPicture\" src={avatar}></img>\r\n            <div className=\"Education\">\r\n              <h2>Education</h2>\r\n              <p>Secondary School of Electrical Engineering</p>\r\n              <p> Bratislava / Slovakia </p>\r\n              <p> 2016-2020</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div className=\"CvContact\">\r\n              <h3>Phone</h3>\r\n              <p>+421 951 421 115</p>\r\n\r\n              <h3>Email</h3>\r\n              <p>tomas.radic00@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n              <h3>Website</h3>\r\n              <a>https://radicc.github.io/Portfolio/</a>\r\n\r\n              <h3>Address</h3>\r\n              <p>Malacky, Slovakia</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div className=\"RightPaper\">\r\n            <div className=\"NameTitul\">\r\n              <h1>TOMÁŠ RADIČ</h1>\r\n              <p>SELFTHOUGHT FRONTEND DEVELOPER</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div className=\"AboutMe\">\r\n              <h3 className=\"titles\">ABOUT ME</h3>\r\n              <p>\r\n                Passionate self-taught student of frontend development trying to\r\n                change profession. Desire to learn and grow in a collaborative\r\n                team environment.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div className=\"AboutMe\">\r\n              <h3 className=\"titles\">WORK EXPERIENCE</h3>\r\n              <p></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div className=\"AboutMe\">\r\n              <h3 className=\"titles\">SOFTWARE SKILL</h3>\r\n              <p>\r\n                ●HTML, ●CSS, ●SASS, ●Javascript, ●React, ●GIT, ●Adobe Photoshop,\r\n                ●Blender\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div className=\"Footer1\">\r\n        <a\r\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer1\"\r\n          href=\"https://github.com/Radicc\"\r\n          target=\"_blank\"\r\n        >\r\n          <img className=\"footerSocial\" src={gitHub} />\r\n          <p className=\"footerText\">GitHub</p>\r\n        </a>\r\n        <a\r\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer2\"\r\n          href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tomas-radicc/\"\r\n          target=\"_blank\"\r\n        >\r\n          <img className=\"footerSocial\" src={linkedIN} />\r\n          <p className=\"footerText\">LinkedIn</p>\r\n        </a>\r\n        <a\r\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer3\"\r\n          href=\"https://twitter.com/TomRadi1\"\r\n          target=\"_blank\"\r\n        >\r\n          <img className=\"footerSocial\" src={twitter} />\r\n          <p className=\"footerText\">Twitter</p>\r\n        </a>\r\n        <a\r\n          className=\"socialFooterContainer4\"\r\n          href=\"https://www.instagram.com/radic.o_o/\"\r\n          target=\"_blank\"\r\n        >\r\n          <img className=\"footerSocial\" src={instagram} />\r\n          <p className=\"footerText\">Instagram</p>\r\n        </a>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div id=\"Contact\" className=\"Footer2\">\r\n        <a href=\"#Contact\" onClick={showContact}>\r\n          MAIL ME NOW!\r\n        </a>\r\n        <img src={Mail} />\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <form\r\n        action=\"https://formsubmit.co/tomas.radic00@gmail.com\"\r\n        method=\"POST\"\r\n        className={props.Mailos}\r\n      >\r\n        <div className=\"contactContainer\">\r\n          <h1>CONTACT ME</h1>\r\n          <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_subject\" value=\"New submission!\"></input>\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"text\"\r\n            id=\"name\"\r\n            name=\"name\"\r\n            placeholder=\"Name\"\r\n            spellCheck=\"false\"\r\n            required\r\n          />\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"email\"\r\n            id=\"email\"\r\n            name=\"email\"\r\n            placeholder=\"Email\"\r\n            spellCheck=\"false\"\r\n            required\r\n          />\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"text\"\r\n            id=\"phone\"\r\n            name=\"phone\"\r\n            placeholder=\"Phone Number\"\r\n            spellCheck=\"false\"\r\n            required\r\n          />\r\n          <textarea\r\n            rows=\"4\"\r\n            id=\"message\"\r\n            name=\"message\"\r\n            placeholder=\"How can i help you?\"\r\n            spellCheck=\"false\"\r\n          ></textarea>\r\n          <div className=\"CVbutton2Container\">\r\n            <button type=\"submit\" className=\"ContactSubmit\">\r\n              <span></span>\r\n              <span></span>\r\n              <span></span>\r\n              <span></span>\r\n              SUBMIT\r\n            </button>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </form>\r\n\r\n      <div className=\"Footer3\">\r\n        <p>© Copyright 2022, Tomas Radic All Rights Reserved.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  );\r\n}\r\n",{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":35,"column":13,"nodeType":"316","endLine":35,"endColumn":62},{"ruleId":"317","severity":1,"message":"318","line":16,"column":6,"nodeType":"319","endLine":16,"endColumn":13,"suggestions":"320"},{"ruleId":"321","severity":1,"message":"322","line":1,"column":17,"nodeType":"323","messageId":"324","endLine":1,"endColumn":26},{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":7,"column":7,"nodeType":"316","endLine":10,"endColumn":9},{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":12,"column":7,"nodeType":"316","endLine":15,"endColumn":9},{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":17,"column":7,"nodeType":"316","endLine":20,"endColumn":9},{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":22,"column":7,"nodeType":"316","endLine":25,"endColumn":9},{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":27,"column":7,"nodeType":"316","endLine":30,"endColumn":9},{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":32,"column":7,"nodeType":"316","endLine":35,"endColumn":9},{"ruleId":"314","severity":1,"message":"315","line":37,"column":7,"nodeType":"316","endLine":40,"endColumn":9},{"ruleId":"3